    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. John,",
        "I am writing this letter to provide you information regarding invitation received to attend the networking conference at Hybrid Company on 24th of July. As, this conference is important for me because I will learn new skills which assists in my specialization.",
        "I have received the invitation as I got award of best performance in networking last year from our company. Hence, this seminar will enhance my knowledge which will be useful at office. Hence, it would also aid company by providing the lecture to my team members and other employees who is interested in this topic.",
